{
  "texts": [
    "MethodologyFigure 1 provides an overview of the research setup presented in this paper.There are basically two parts to perform the analysis.",
    "Part 1 is the related company selection.",
    "The definition of a related company is broad.",
    "However, in this research paper, we define the related companies as the companies which frequently co-occur in news articles concerning the target company because if a company frequently appears in news articles about the target company, it is likely that the two companies are connected.",
    "By applying Named Entity Recognition (NER), we can extract the companies from the news articles of the target company."
  ]
}